  "2237320": {
    "name": "Dwarf Delve",
    "steam_appid": 2237320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/ac29f77ec9ee6c9d03d4815c77909bbf.poster.avif?t=1770654593\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/ac29f77ec9ee6c9d03d4815c77909bbf.webm?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/ac29f77ec9ee6c9d03d4815c77909bbf.mp4?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>Dwarf Delve</strong>，Delveling！在这款随机生成的采掘类 Roguelite 中，成为你注定要成为的矮人。深入危险的矿井，寻找珍贵的矿石和隐藏在大地深处的宝藏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>勇闯深渊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/e27a73e2451e963f9ddd1efa76dd60e8.poster.avif?t=1770654593\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/e27a73e2451e963f9ddd1efa76dd60e8.webm?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/e27a73e2451e963f9ddd1efa76dd60e8.mp4?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挥舞你的 <i>Battlemallet</i>，抓起每一块珍贵的矿石、宝藏和传奇遗物，只要你的双手能承受。那些古老的洞穴已沉睡数百年……但现在不再如此！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战略性地铺设轨道，并利用手边的一切工具，将辛苦开采的矿石高效运送到安全之处。借助灯笼和照明弹穿越黑暗，照亮前方道路，揭示隐藏在阴影中的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收获你的战利品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/73bcf3ed838e0826e9ccba28b0dbbfea.poster.avif?t=1770654593\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/73bcf3ed838e0826e9ccba28b0dbbfea.webm?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/73bcf3ed838e0826e9ccba28b0dbbfea.mp4?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心！这些矿井中布满了看不见的危险和早已被遗忘的陷阱。一次失误就可能让你丧命——或者更糟，失去战利品！锻造关键物品，如支撑梁、梯子，甚至探照灯。无论如何，务必确保头顶的安全。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>活着离开！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/efeee823e56551a94f3686607632536f.poster.avif?t=1770654593\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/efeee823e56551a94f3686607632536f.webm?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237320/extras/efeee823e56551a94f3686607632536f.mp4?t=1770654593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当采掘完成后，回到你温馨的矮人小屋好好休息吧！精炼你在探险中收集的矿石，将它们转化为宝贵的物品。利用新财富购买各种装备和工具，强化你的能力，让你攻击更强、移动更快，并能携带更多战利品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成的冒险。没有两个矿井是相同的！探索每一个角落，寻找最稀有的矿石和宝藏，并在塌方前带回它们！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的工具和装备选择。从你可靠的 Battlemallet 到最基础的灯笼，充分利用优势，延缓这些古老洞穴的必然崩塌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>升级</i>？每件装备都可以根据你的风格进行升级和自定义；用强化工具打击更有力，或者用便携探照灯驱散黑暗。你来决定每次探险的方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的住所！从地毯到墙面装饰！发现新物品并挂在家中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用资源兑换金币，并通过购买新技能和特权来提升你的 Delveling。移动更快，攻击更强，携带更多战利品！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更聪明地工作！铺设轨道并建造矿车网络，为你搬运和存储那些沉重的矿石！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将工具固定在工具挂钩上，在你挥锤开采时解放双手。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你准备好回应深渊的召唤了吗？进入一个勇者得财富的世界，在那里，深渊为足够勇敢去探索的人藏有难以想象的财富。欢迎登船，Delveling！</strong></p>",
